### 1. 创建订单（注解式）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/create/annotation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1001,
  "productName": "iPhone 15 Pro",
  "productPrice": 7999.00,
  "quantity": 1
}

### 2. 创建订单（编程式）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/create/programmatic
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1002,
  "productName": "MacBook Pro 16",
  "productPrice": 19999.00,
  "quantity": 1
}

### 3. 查询订单（替换{orderNo}为实际订单号）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/ORD1733735123456ABCD1234

### 4. 批量创建订单测试
